# Terraform AWS ALB Project

## Description
This project creates:
- Custom VPC
- Public Subnets
- Internet Gateway & Route Table
- EC2 instances
- Application Load Balancer
- Target Group
- S3 Bucket

## Architecture
ALB → EC2 (Web Server 1 & 2)

## How to Run
```bash
terraform init
terraform validate
terraform plan
terraform apply

